summary: ...GABRIELLE MOVING QUICKLY EAST-NORTHEASTWARD ACROSS THE SUBTROPICAL ATLANTIC... ...HURRICANE WARNING IN EFFECT FOR THE AZORES... As of 11:00 AM AST Wed Sep 24 the center of Gabrielle was located near 36.0, -48.7 with movement ENE at 25 mph. The minimum central pressure was 962 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 110 mph.
